    "note": "PER-ELEMENT PALETTES: demonstrates IdeogramElementBuilder + IdeogramElementCollector. Two reference images each produce a <=5 color element palette (IdeogramElementPalette), each wired into an IdeogramElementBuilder's color_palette as the palette for one spatial region. A third builder adds a text overlay element with no palette. The collector assembles all three into a compositional_deconstruction block (background + elements) and reports overlapping text boxes. Boxes use [ymin, xmin, ymax, xmax], integers 0-1000. The block is ready to paste under 'compositional_deconstruction' in a full Ideogram 4 prompt. ShowText nodes are optional (ComfyUI-Custom-Scripts) and only display strings."
